  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This evaluation is being conducted to determine user perception of a new flat one-piece skin
      barrier compared to their normal barrier.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Design:

      This is a multi-site, unblinded, historically controlled assessment of a one-piece flat skin
      barrier. Study barriers are CE-marked. Approximately 30 subjects are enrolled in the UK.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
